icons.title: Supported icons
apply.general: Icon Packs can be applied with many different Launchers on Android-Devices. If you don't have one, the app will show you which ones you can install.
apply.galaxy.title: Galaxy-Devices
apply.galaxy.paragraph: With this one you'll get the best experience. Here you can apply the pack directly with Theme Park. (If you use a custom launcher you should apply it there too to get the icons displayed correctly)
paragraph.description: We create transparent icons that are visible on any background. To accomplish this we outline every image with a black outline.
paragraph.info: If you want to create your own Icon-Pack you can read this article.
icons.smart-things.info: The icon-pack's logo is inspired from this one.
icons.lawnchair-settings.info: The Settings for the Lawnchair-Laucher which you can use to display this icon-pack.
icons.lawnchair.info: Laucher which you can use to display this icon-pack.
icons.add.info:
If you want to add more icons feel free to open an issue or a pull request on the Github Repository.
You can also send a icon-request (from the app) to miep_hd@froxot.com.
icons.f-droid.info: Download the icon-pack from F-Droid.
icons.aurora-store.info: Download the icon-pack from the Aurora Store.
icons.google-play-store.info: Download the icon-pack from Google Play Store.
